abstract: The Economic Report of the President said the rate would fall to 9.2 percent next year and remain well over 6 percent until 2015.
snippet: The Economic Report of the President said the rate would fall to 9.2 percent next year and remain well over 6 percent until 2015.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON  The Obama administration projected Thursday that the unemployment rate would fall this year by only a little, if at all, and would remain well over 6 percent until 2015.
